snippet.textDisplay:
Your not wrong. I’m not a professional fighter. I am a guy who came up fighting in the streets of Chicago and later on, LA burbs though and trained in martial arts most of my life. I currently teach martial arts “albeit traditional more” and in my assessment I feel Conor is the best striker I have ever seen. His confidence is something to marvel at. To say it more accurately his self belief is something to marvel at. As a striker myself I admire why he does.

The reality is that I would kick Conors ass without even blinking but that’s because I would have a baseball bat, and maybe a handgun lol.

Thanks my friend for keeping it real. It’s not easy for many to keep it real because of being real means giving certain people props you will no doubt be called a fan boy, but the real one don’t care Chael, and your a real one.
